                    I am <strong class="text-slate-700 font-medium">Luca Fuster</strong>, an Engineer student. I am passionate about technology, innovation, and leadership. Through my experiences in student organizations and technical projects, I've developed a strong foundation in both technical skills and team management.
                </p>
