                    I am currently looking for a <strong class="text-slate-700 font-medium">6-month internship</strong> for <strong class="text-slate-700 font-medium">summer-autumn 2026</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="/cv.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-slate-500 font-medium neu-shadow neu-hover hover:text-violet-500">
